title: Disbursements in the Gulf of Mexico
content:
Today, if you’re depressed, or want to kill some cancer cells, good information for you. <!--more--> Insights on what causes a lot of our chronic viral infections.
And, a nutrient for improving cognitive function in music.
On the environmental segment: What’s happened to so many people down in the Gulf of Mexico area as a result of disbursements.
Also, carbon pollution up to two million pounds per second.
 And more!
